1
00:00:00,630 --> 00:00:01,750
Makoto!

2
00:00:01,750 --> 00:00:03,800
Wait, you...?

3
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:12,010
Oh, so you went to college together?

4
00:00:12,010 --> 00:00:13,430
What a coincidence!

5
00:00:13,430 --> 00:00:15,220
Yeah, I was surprised too.

6
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:18,810
Of all the people I've trained,

7
00:00:18,810 --> 00:00:20,650
he's one of the best.

8
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:22,940
But we can't let rookies get cocky.

9
00:00:23,690 --> 00:00:24,570
Keep this a secret, okay?

10
00:00:24,570 --> 00:00:27,030
Okay, I won't say a word.

11
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:28,820
Excuse me.

12
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:30,030
Yes?

13
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:31,030
Wakami-san!

14
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,370
They need you to check something on set.

15
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:33,280
On my way.

16
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:36,490
Remember, keep what I said a secret.

17
00:00:36,490 --> 00:00:37,660
Got it.

18
00:00:42,250 --> 00:00:43,630
What were you guys talking about?

19
00:00:43,630 --> 00:00:44,840
It's a secret!

20
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:46,130
Huh? Come on, tell me!

21
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:48,170
No way.
Get back to work.

22
00:00:48,170 --> 00:00:49,380
Come on, just tell me.

23
00:00:49,380 --> 00:00:51,180
Go back to work.

24
00:00:51,180 --> 00:00:53,180
Fine, but you have to tell me.

25
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:55,010
Why do I have to tell you?

26
00:00:58,810 --> 00:01:02,150
I've got to put this fire out...
